article.description: — JT Shumate had 19 points and 10 rebounds, Setric Millner Jr. added 18 points and 12 rebounds and Toledo held off Tulane 68-67 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Toledo narrowly beats Tulane 68-67
article.story: NASSAU, Bahamas -- — JT Shumate had 19 points and 10 rebounds, Setric Millner Jr. added 18 points and 12 rebounds and Toledo held off Tulane 68-67 on Tuesday night. Ryan Rollins chipped in 16 points for the Rockets (4-1).
